Benefits of Belonging to Members Club at Marco!
Golf Club Membership
Joining The Members Club at Marco offers more than just exceptional golf. It’s an invitation to a world of comfort and exclusivity, where members enjoy a luxurious lifestyle. Whether you're seeking relaxation or recreation, this membership offers it all.
Private Access
You'll gain access to private, members-only areas, complete with a game room, pool, lounge, veranda, private dining room, and an executive meeting room. These spaces are ideal for hosting parties, casual gatherings, or simply unwinding with friends after a day on the course.
Two Championship Courses
Golf enthusiasts are in for a treat with two resort private courses. The Rookery Course, with its Platinum Paspalum turf, provides a premier golfing experience, while the Hammock Bay Course, seamlessly integrated into the natural surroundings, offers another 18 holes of scenic golf. Combined, these courses deliver 36 holes of world-class golf for members to enjoy.
Exclusive Social Events
The Members Club at Marco offers a dynamic calendar filled with social events and exciting tournaments year-round. From themed pool parties and dining to friendly golf and tennis competitions, these gatherings provide members with opportunities to connect, compete, and enjoy the  club experience.
Join the waitlist
Resort Benefits
Members enjoy exclusive perks at JW Marriott Marco Island Beach Resort, including a private Member's Cove beach section, access to multiple pools, Spa by JW amenities, complimentary wellness classes, and 20% discounts on retail, spa, and dining.
